snippet.title: Witchfire Summer Game Fest 2022 Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Epic Games Store: https://www.epicgames.com/p/witchfire-db273e
Info on Early Access in our blog post: https://www.theastronauts.com/2022/06/witchfire-summer-games-fest-2022-trailer/

Armed with strange weapons and forbidden pagan magic, hunt a powerful witch holding the key to your salvation. Witchfire is a dark fantasy roguelite first-person shooter from the creators of
Painkiller, Bulletstorm, and The Vanishing of Ethan Carter.
